{"tid":546104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信 / 電話 要求財爺派錢","createTime":"2018-01-31T08:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T16:48:00.000Z","uid":49443,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"55e2b2d8d171e1c40f780ee6e5922e4802bffaa9","tid":546104,"uid":49443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:06:56.000Z","msg":"政府有錢就身痕 起大白象工程 送錢比大陸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又話起多d公屋 幫人上樓 最後咪又比新移民蝻住哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計我話派錢最實際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一齊寫信要求派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特區政府現正就二零一八／一九年度《財政預算案》展開諮詢。歡迎各位市民透過電郵（budget@fstb.gov.hk）、電話（2810 3768）或傳真（2147 5770）提交意見。市民亦<br />\n可將意見郵寄至香港添馬添美道2號政府總部24樓財政預算案諮詢支援小組。"},{"pid":"1e3ab5b56aec39155a8c8ec2b5fe66a90997bd27","tid":546104,"uid":156902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:19:50.000Z","msg":"Angel方加"},{"pid":"9333b373b8f30d0bd1525cb2c5fe87caba7c9352","tid":546104,"uid":49443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694ddde97add6999e775f45dab800aa05a499b00","tid":546104,"uid":96941,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"你傻架"},{"pid":"6230f09da432055a5a96b2ee31403d8113138f5b","tid":546104,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3c8ede3b26ecaa1a615718994c3b25d7501e864","tid":546104,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"明日打電話去要求派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0d4d